The paper also discusses the use of token-forwarding algorithms, which are commonly used in the field of Networked Information Systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the complexity of the problem and the use of randomized algorithms, which are topics that fall under the category of Information Theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper discusses the dissemination of information in a network, which is a topic that falls under the category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
